    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who specialize in making mirrors, which are objects with a highly polished surface designed to reflect images; often intended for those who make mirrors of glass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
